{"tid":1474524,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"真係好嬲！你地班冷氣軍師亂咁叫人罷買害番自己人，真正要抵制果d又無人抵制","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T08:06:59.000Z","uid":255497,"like":11,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"3ace1042d65409fc7c6f29f567c0574b55b3b6fa","tid":1474524,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">   我有朋友係開珍珠奶茶，同時間佢次次遊行都有企出黎，仲keep住會捐錢俾物資組。前幾日因為大陸代理果邊亂講野搞到上左罷買list，但佢明明係深黃同路人，無端端就俾同自己同一信念既人杯葛罷買，佢覺得賺少左錢都其次，佢最撚嬲係聽到d路人話佢地奶共，咁樣同果班on9藍絲亂信網路流言屈9人有咩分別???<br />\n我相信香港人十個有最少七八個都係同路人，即係你地而家罷買緊果個list有八成都係無辜。<br />\n點解香港人而家要變到咁唔理性呢？<br />\n明明有一間賺緊香港人錢交緊稅俾共產黨，出糧俾公安同解放軍，老闆藍(紅)撚到仆街，但又無人話要抵制佢？仲日日成班港女排緊隊？<br />\n<br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n    </span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你班仆街訓撚醒未阿</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXFQVbE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXFQVbE.jpg&h=d5162b67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fb4KfbF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffb4KfbF.jpg&h=ecd69afd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29cbf8a64a273e23a368bc69ed538fa46bff1f4f","tid":1474524,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"644befa924024f63ded25de5e4174a3d359b2dca","tid":1474524,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail